00:08:51.340 --> 00:08:54.180
They also used words like "depressing,"

00:08:54.940 --> 00:08:56.516
"humiliating,"

00:08:56.540 --> 00:08:57.740
"degrading."

00:08:58.260 --> 00:09:01.340
The young men never used that language.

00:09:02.260 --> 00:09:05.636
So when young women
report sexual satisfaction levels

00:09:05.660 --> 00:09:08.580
that are equal to
or greater than young men's --

00:09:09.260 --> 00:09:10.500
and they do in research --

00:09:11.260 --> 00:09:12.660
that can be deceptive.

00:09:13.460 --> 00:09:17.076
If a girl goes into an encounter
hoping that it won't hurt,

00:09:17.100 --> 00:09:19.116
wanting to feel close to her partner

00:09:19.140 --> 00:09:21.180
and expecting him to have an orgasm,

00:09:21.980 --> 00:09:24.340
