00:09:28.220 --> 00:09:29.556
or wanting him to be happy,

00:09:29.580 --> 00:09:32.104
and orgasm isn't the only
measure of an experience ...

00:09:33.380 --> 00:09:34.620
but absence of pain --

00:09:35.580 --> 00:09:39.100
that's a very low bar
for your own sexual fulfillment.

00:09:40.820 --> 00:09:43.036
Listening to all of this
and thinking about it,

00:09:43.060 --> 00:09:48.356
