a kind of psychological clitoridectomy

00:09:48.380 --> 00:09:49.620
on American girls.

00:09:50.180 --> 00:09:51.476
Starting in infancy,

00:09:51.500 --> 00:09:55.316
parents of baby boys are more likely
to name all their body parts,

00:09:55.340 --> 00:09:57.420
at least they'll say,
"here's your pee-pee."

00:09:58.100 --> 00:10:01.276
