00:10:04.780 --> 00:10:06.116
(Laughter)

00:10:06.140 --> 00:10:09.596
There's no better way
to make something unspeakable

00:10:09.620 --> 00:10:10.820
than not to name it.

00:10:12.100 --> 00:10:14.516
Then kids go into
their puberty education classes

00:10:14.540 --> 00:10:17.620
