00:11:04.260 --> 00:11:05.460
Here's something, though.

00:11:06.140 --> 00:11:09.316
Girls' investment
in their partner's pleasure remains

00:11:09.340 --> 00:11:11.780
regardless of the gender of the partner.

00:11:12.500 --> 00:11:14.756
So in same-sex encounters,

00:11:14.780 --> 00:11:17.260
