00:13:44.660 --> 00:13:48.716
is if we talk to young people
more about sex --

00:13:48.740 --> 00:13:51.076
if we normalize those discussions,

00:13:51.100 --> 00:13:53.996
integrating them into everyday life,

00:13:54.020 --> 00:13:57.556
