in a different way --

00:13:57.580 --> 00:14:00.356
the way we mostly have changed

00:14:00.380 --> 00:14:03.020
in the way that we talk
about women in the public realm.

00:14:03.540 --> 00:14:08.116
Consider a survey
of 300 randomly chosen girls

00:14:08.140 --> 00:14:10.516
from a Dutch and an American university,

00:14:10.540 --> 00:14:12.276
